description: Enclosed by plain wooden walls, the shop features a worn rug in the center of its wooden floor.  A tattered merchant permit hangs under the wooden ceiling.  Right near the front is a shell-lined bamboo counter and an oversized sea chest.

Plain wooden walls rise from an unfinished wooden floor.  Just above a worn rug hangs a tattered merchant permit, and an uneven wooden ceiling completes the picture.  A plain wooden table and a shell-lined bamboo counter stand side by side in the middle of the room.

A tattered merchant permit hangs on one of the plain wooden walls, and an uneven wooden ceiling rises overhead.  A worn rug sits in one corner of an unfinished wooden floor.  There is an aqua-hued seaglass display on one side of the shop and a splintered cargo crate on the other.
title: [Hamehela's Magic Shoppe]
